'As it was, he was just badly shaken.'

Dc Heaney is appealing for witnesses to the incident which happened near Regents Street, at around 3.35am on Saturday May 10.

Scotland Yard said the attacker told the victim he was Algerian.

He was wearing a dark baseball-type jacket, dark blue jeans and a black baseball cap, and was described as bald with stubble, 5ft 8ins and of muscular build.

